snippet.title: Thousands Lining Up For Nude Restaurant

localized.description:
A new restaurant in London allows customers to dine in the nude. It will have clothed and non-clothed sections. Hasan Piker, Grace Baldridge & Sam Schacher discuss on The Young Turks. Do you agree with TYT’s opinion? Tell us what you think in the comment section below.

Read more here: http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/london-gets-first-naked-restaurant-waiting-list-already-at-5000-a6992696.html

"I don’t know about you, but if there’s one thing that’s always bugged me about eating in restaurants it's having to wear clothes. Why stain them, when you can imbibe as the Romans might, naked, with sauce and wine spilling all down your body?

This is presumably the gap in the market The Bunyadi is hoping to fill, a pop-up restaurant coming to London this summer for three months.

‘Enter a secret Pangea-like world,’ its website promises, 'free from phones, electric lights and even clothing (optional) and revisit the beginning where everything was fresh, free and unadulterated from the trappings of modern life.’*

Read more here: http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/that-london-naked-restaurant-now-has-a-waiting-list-of-30000-a7005241.html

Hosts: Cenk Uygur

Cast: Cenk Uygur
